{
  "stem": "21004.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were Polish people there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the Polish people were not so bad, because this was Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The Polish people got a little suffering too for us, because the Ukrainian didn't like the Polacks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we came out, and we ask him where's the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They say go the other way, and there you can pick up the wires and sneak in to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We pick up the wires.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He let me in, and then I let him in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We came to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he ask a couple of Jewish policemen, Jew-- there was Jewish-- in the ghetto was always Jewish security, Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If they need to take to work, they just say give me so many-- so many Jews to work in this place, work-- so they didn't come into the ghetto and grab people.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they have-- there was a Judenrat, call it a Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A president, and you had police where you send out-- taking the Jews to work inside-- there were all difference kind of places where they needed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we-- he found-- he found his cousin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the cousin took us in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was living with other people also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Crowded.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Very overcrowded.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Every ghetto was overcrowded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had some food there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We stay there one day till it got dark.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The second night, we can go out from them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wouldn't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's all happened like in the month of-- beginning of December or October or November, the end of November, something like this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The year, 1940-- '42. 1942.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "December, 1942.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We went out at night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And later, we went out from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
